{
  "texts": [
    "Third, in addition to requiring clarity from the researcher, ChatGPT took on the role of a research partner or interlocuter supplying additional insights into the texts by observing things we missed in our human analyses.",
    "Fourth, ChatGPT provided a robustness check similar to inter-coder reliability by corroborating and challenging the researcher's interpretations and conclusions, prompting the researchers to reexamine their conclusions and return to the data to find more empirical support for analyses.",
    "In addition to coding, classification, and thematic analysis, LLMs can be prompted to provide a higher-level analysis of the data.",
    "In our experience with higher-level analytical queries, we found that LLMs are more limited and cannot be relied on for a full analysis.",
    "The human researcher is still the key to good interpretive research."
  ]
}